Class Constants.RobotMap.PodConfig

java.lang.Object
frc.robot.Constants.RobotMap.PodConfig
Enclosing class:
Constants.RobotMap
public static final class Constants.RobotMap.PodConfig extends Object
PodConfig holds configuration for a single swerve pod. Includes motor IDs, encoder offsets, and position.
